product.name: Cat Door for Wall, Energy Efficient Pet Door with Steel Frame, Telescoping Tunnel, Double Magnetic Flaps and Two Sliding Lock Panels, Easy to Install, Milky White, Small
product.bullet_points:
• Hands-Free: Give your furry friends true independence with this wall cat door, allowing pets to freely come and go on their own schedule — no more anxious waiting at the door or disrupted routines.
• Sturdy Steel Construction: Built with rust-proof steel framing, this cat door for wall withstands aggressive chewing, clawing, and decade-level wear — ideal even for powerful breeds.
• Fits Any Wall: Accommodating walls 4" to 8" thick (brick/drywall/wood), this pet door's 13 9/10" x 9 2/5" frame and 9 1/4" x 6 1/2" opening comfortably fit pets up to 22 lbs. Its neutral white finish blends seamlessly with any decor.
• All-Weather Defense System: Engineered for extreme conditions, our kitty door features double magnetic flaps and dual sliding lock panels that create an impenetrable seal against rain, wind, and snow while reducing HVAC costs.
• 3-Mode Safety Control: Secure your home via sliding panels: Full Open for free access, Full Lock for security, or Partial Open to contain pets while allowing airflow—all on one pet door for wall.
• Quick DIY Install & Clean: Install your pet door for wall effortlessly using our detailed guide and precise cutting template. Plus, swapping out flaps is a breeze for quick cleaning or replacements.
• Support Guaranteed: Our dedicated customer service team is ready to assist with any questions about setup or use – ensuring a smooth experience from day one.
